    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you are not so good at remembering shortcut mappings, you have the option of installing <a href=\"https://plugins.jetbrains.com/plugin/13931-json-formatter\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">JSON Formatter plugin</a> which allow you to minify and format and also verify a JSON file.</p>\n"
